Package: glatar
Title: Shiny app that interfaces with GLATAR database
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Benjamin L.", "Hlina", , "benjamin.hlinal@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This app has the ability to upload (i.e., 
             if you are a contributing member), map, view raw data (i.e., 
             if you are a contributing member), view summarised data, 
             and view scatter plots of the raw data and can be found at  <https://glatar.org>. 
